file.name: F-secure-endpoint_protection_api.yaml
file.content:
basePath: /mp/v1
components:
  securitySchemes:
    ApiKeyAuth:
      in: header
      name: X-API-Key
      type: apiKey
host: psblive.psb-stg.fsapi.com
info:
  contact:
    email: azgarech@linuxtrack.net
    name: '@azgaviperr'
    url: https://azgaviperr.github.io/
  description: A multi-purpose API that is used to manage computers, monitor events,
    list subscriptions, control various endpoint protection features, and generate
    reports.
  title: Endpoint Protection API
  version: '1.0'
  x-categories:
  - Assets
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /authentication/login:
    post:
      description: Access to Endpoint Protection API is granted using user name and
        password-based authentication in combination with an API key. The obtained
        token is used in the subsequent requests.
      operationId: Authenticate
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        example: "{\n  \"password\": \"${password}\",\n  \"username\": \"${username}\"\
          \n}"
        in: body
        multiline: true
        name: body
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Header generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        example: application/json
        in: header
        multiline: false
        name: Content-Type
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Header generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        example: application/json
        in: header
        multiline: false
        name: Accept
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          example:
            example: "{\n  \"password\": \"${password}\",\n  \"username\": \"${username}\"\
              \n}"
        description: Generated by Shuffler.io
        required: false
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Authenticate
  /companies/{companyId}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve company information by the given ID.
      operationId: Get_company_details
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get company details
  /companies/{companyId}/computers:
    get:
      description: List computers of a company with the given ID.
      operationId: List_company_computers
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List company computers
  /companies/{companyId}/computers/{computerId}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve computer information by the given ID.
      operationId: Get_company_computer_details
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: computerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get company computer details
  /companies/{companyId}/computers/{computerId}/infections:
    get:
      description: List found infections for a computer with the given ID.
      operationId: List_found_infections_for_a_company_computer
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: action
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: infectionType
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: quarantined
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: computerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List found infections for a company computer
  /companies/{companyId}/computers/{computerId}/missing-software-updates:
    get:
      description: List software updates missing from a company computer with given
        ID.
      operationId: List_missing_software_updates
      parameters:
      - description: Filter used for searching for software updates with the given
          software name.
        in: query
        name: softwareName
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for software updates with the given
          software vendor.
        in: query
        name: softwareVendor
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for software updates with the given
          software service pack.
        in: query
        name: softwareServicePack
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for software updates with the given
          category.
        in: query
        name: category
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for software updates with the given
          severity.
        in: query
        name: severity
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: sort
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: computerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List missing software updates
  /companies/{companyId}/infections:
    get:
      description: List found infections for a company with the given ID.
      operationId: List_found_infections_for_a_company
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List found infections for a company
  /companies/{companyId}/reports/computers:
    get:
      description: Provides information in CSV format on the computers owned by the
        given company.
      operationId: Get_company_computers_report
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get company computers report
  /companies/{companyId}/subscriptions:
    get:
      description: List subscriptions that belong to a company with the given ID.
      operationId: List_company_subscriptions
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List company subscriptions
  /companies/{companyId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve subscription information by the given ID.
      operationId: Get_company_subscription_details
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: subscriptionId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get company subscription details
  /companies/{companyId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/removed-computers:
    delete:
      description: Removes computers from the subscription-specific blacklist, allowing
        computers to register and connect to PSB again.
      operationId: Remove_computers_from_subscription
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: subscriptionId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Remove computers from subscription
  /companies/{companyUuid}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve company information by the given UUID.
      operationId: Get_company_details_by_UUID
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyUuid
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get company details by UUID
  /companies/{companyUuid}/security-events:
    get:
      description: List security events for a company with the given ID.
      operationId: List_security_events_for_a_company
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyUuid
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List security events for a company
  /companies/{companyUuid}/subscriptions:
    get:
      description: List subscriptions that belong to a company with the given UUID.
      operationId: List_company_subscriptions_by_UUID
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: companyUuid
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List company subscriptions by UUID
  /partners/{partnerId}/companies:
    get:
      description: List companies of a partner with the given ID.
      operationId: List_partner_companies
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: page
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: perPage
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: perPage
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List partner companies
  /partners/{partnerId}/computers:
    get:
      description: List computers of a partner with the given ID.
      operationId: List_partner_computers
      parameters:
      - description: Category of computer information to return.
        in: query
        name: category
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: issue
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given overallProtection
          state.
        in: query
        name: overallProtection
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given automaticUpdates
          state.
        in: query
        name: automaticUpdates
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given virusProtection
          state.
        in: query
        name: virusProtection
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given softwareUpdates
          state.
        in: query
        name: softwareUpdates
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given subscription
          key.
        in: query
        name: subscriptionKey
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given label
          value.
        in: query
        name: label
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given firewall
          state.
        in: query
        name: firewall
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given real-time
          scanning state.
        in: query
        name: realTimeScanning
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given application
          control state.
        in: query
        name: applicationControl
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers with the given client
          type.
        in: query
        name: clientType
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filter used for searching for computers applicable for given
          profile type.
        in: query
        name: profileType
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: sort
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: order
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Search term.
        in: query
        name: q
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List partner computers
  /partners/{partnerId}/infections:
    get:
      description: List found infections for a partner with the given ID.
      operationId: List_found_infections_for_a_partner
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: sort
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: The earliest timestamp of the infections (aka Client Date) that
          should be returned
        in: query
        name: from
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: The latest timestamp of the infections (aka Client Date) that
          should be retuned
        in: query
        name: to
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List found infections for a partner
  /partners/{partnerId}/reports/computers:
    get:
      description: Provides information in CSV format on the computers managed by
        the given partner.
      operationId: Get_partner_computers_report
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get partner computers report
  /partners/{partnerId}/subscriptions:
    get:
      description: List subscriptions that that match the search criteria.
      operationId: List_partner_subscriptions
      parameters:
      - description: Filter used for searching subscriptions with 'expirationTimestamp'
          matching a specific time period.
        in: query
        name: expiration
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Filters by product type
        in: query
        name: products
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: query
        name: sort
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List partner subscriptions
  /partners/{partnerId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}:
    get:
      description: Retrieve subscription information by the given ID.
      operationId: Get_partner_subscription_details
      parameters:
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: subscriptionId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: Get partner subscription details
  /partners/{partnerUuid}/security-events:
    get:
      description: List security events for a partner with the given ID.
      operationId: List_security_events_for_a_partner
      parameters:
      - description: Value pointing to the beginning of the events page to be fetched.
        in: query
        name: cursor
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Severity of event.
        in: query
        name: severity
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Engine that triggered an event.
        in: query
        name: engine
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Device's agentId, e.g. 35a6fbca-acc8-11eb-8529-0242ac130003
        in: query
        name: agentId
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Id of an event (unique).
        in: query
        name: eventId
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      - description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
        in: path
        name: partnerUuid
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      requestBody:
        content: {}
      responses:
        default:
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: ''
                type: string
          description: default
      summary: List security events for a partner
